Site Deployment:
https://mtdeweese.github.io/iws-p1/index.html

Deployed using github.

Site Purpose:

Discuss the book I am currently reading, my general taste in books, and provide recommendations for books.

3 Pages:
index - Introduction to me and my type of book
current - Information about my current book
recommendation - Recommendations for books

also have:
recommendation.js - picks and loads the random book recommendation selection


To update the website:
For normal content:
edit the html file for the corresponding page or the styles.css file for design changes
To add/edit the recommendations edit recommendation.js

Then push changes to the repository and it will automatically deploy with the changes.